quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  2,49,aur ( hamaray un ahsanat ko yaad karo ) jab hum ne tum ko qomِ firaon se nijaat bakhsh woh ( log ) tum ko bara dukh dete they tumahray biton ko to qatal kar daaltay they aur baityon ko zindah rehne dete they aur is mein tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se barri ( sakht ) azmaish thi
  2,50,aur jab hum ne tumahray liye darya ko phaar diya tum ko nijaat di aur firaon ki qoum ko ghark kar diya aur tum dekh hi to rahay they
  2,51,aur jab hum ne moose se chalees raat ka wadakiya to tum ne un ke peechay bichhre ko ( mabood ) muqarrar kar liya aur tum zulm kar rahay they
  2,52,"phir is ke baad hum ne tum ko maaf kar diya, taakay tum shukar karo"
  2,53,"aur jab hum ne moose ko kitaab aur moajezae inayat kiye, taakay tum hadaayat haasil karo"
  2,54,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke bhayyo, tum ne bichhre ko ( mabood ) thehranay mein ( bara ) zulmkiya hai, to apne peda karne walay ke agay tauba karo aur apne tain halaak kar daalo. tumahray khaaliq ke nazdeek tumahray haq mein yahi behtar hai. phir is ne tumhara qasoor maaf kar diya. woh be shak maaf karne wala ( aur ) sahib reham hai"
  2,55,"aur jab tum ne ( moose ) se kaha ke moose, jab taq hum khuda ko samnay nah dekh len ge, tum par imaan nahi layein ge, to tum ko bijli ne aa ghaira aur tum dekh rahay they"
  2,56,"phir mout aa jaane ke baad hum ne tum ko azsrِ no zindah kar diya, taakay ahsaan manu"
  2,57,"aur baadal ka tum par saya kiye rakha aur ( tumahray liye ) mann o salwa utaartay rahay ke jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko ataa farmai hain, un ko khao ( piyo ) magar tumahray buzurgon ne un nematon ki kuch qader nah jani ( aur ) woh hamara kuch nahi bgarhte they balkay apna hi nuqsaan karte they"
